{"tid":1697304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民陣×五大學生會11.24區選日搞百萬集會？","createTime":"2019-11-06T18:37:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T12:12:50.000Z","uid":167548,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"39e5b148a672cbb81a03190776325826c1a727e8","tid":1697304,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T18:37:28.000Z","msg":"前日出文叫大家搞11.10 五大集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n但是比人用要開花為由/非搞手Ban<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得確時間上安排有o的急<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sF3bFkd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsF3bFkd.png&h=d17969fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote> 連仔 求 DEL POST<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1693753\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1693753</a><br />\n【澄清】1110 五大集會 並不舉行！百屌成材！繼續遍地開花！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1693745\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1693745</a></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>大部份手足BUYo架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (500 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> vs +70負評)</strong></span><br />\n但是有幾位手足話大方向11.10商場攬炒戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班人屈埋做狗做五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話是叫大家去大學預約被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n11.10 和平紀念日 去中環 和平紀念碑 有活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">好撚辛鳩苦呀</span> 話要開花 話我是驚犬)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n11.17 Xavi巴搞o既東歐集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n11.24 區選投票日<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">重點嚟啦</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n民陣是你出手o既時候啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<br />\n區選近排不斷爆出種票疑雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇下佢點抽起民主派選票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>(100萬人集會 = 100 萬張選票)</strong></span><br />\n(沒記錯睇過個POST, 民主派票源得~40萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;總投票率 ~40%<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n上午地區投完票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下午<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全世界</span></span></strong>入五大圍爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n遊行集合地點可唔可以係大學？(1600 正評)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/esRePS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/esRePS</a><blockquote><br />\n&lsquo;維園集合就放tg入去<br />\n大學集合會唔會都敢放？<br />\n放左又國際頭條&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>當然呢個是動議啦, 你地自已諗呢句掂唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">「<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>(100萬人集會 = 100 萬張選票)</strong></span>」</span></strong></span><br />\n香港人信任區選點票公平公開公正嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就投完返屋企等港共政權乖乖比議席你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><br />\n民陣&times;五大學生會11.24區選日搞百萬集會</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uK9aV1T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuK9aV1T.png&h=585dd529&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d18b26255348fca13312684800d8484ef415a4e2","tid":1697304,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T18:38:04.000Z","msg":"夜晚少人, 幫手share開去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71df5f2538eecc254c2fbced35d6db3a199d71fe","tid":1697304,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T18:38:28.000Z","msg":"當然投完票, 先好去曬馬集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29495b5c566fd42a677eb0249439ac8ac4248540","tid":1697304,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T18:38:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">「100萬人集會 = 100 萬張選票」</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a920bcf985211033972d578831103c9b90aad86b","tid":1697304,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T18:42:06.000Z","msg":"當然我驚當日曬馬少人會難睇, 自爆其短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&nbsp;所以尚處於討論階段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即使有100萬人參加集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦可能因為沒留足全程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人流加加減減下好似10.14人權法得13萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa0f933648d8456e4ef098d13aab49c6c010741","tid":1697304,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T18:46:04